						               													<description>Four new cards to use in your games of FUSE.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;During setup, designate two areas on the playing surface: one for inactive tools cards, and one for active tools cards.  Shuffle the four tool cards, then select two of them at random and place them in the inactive area, face up.  Return the two remaining tools cards to the game box.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;During the game, players may allocate their chosen dice to the tools cards in the inactive area.  When all spaces on a tool card are filled with dice, return those dice to the bag and move that tool to the active area.  That tools card can now be used at any time.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;To use a tool card, carry out the listed ability, then flip the card face down.  Each card can only be used once a game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Note: When rerolling the unused dice at the end of a round,  you are never required to remove dice that have been placed on tool cards.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Originally contained in Level Up Loot: One&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
